reviewText: I freaking love Inuyasha. It's my favorite Anime series, and one of my first one to watch. I really enjoyed this movie especially when Sesshomaru kicked butt, and the ending part of the movies as well. I was happy to buy this movie and it came with a really amazing coin. <3 So I would totally buy this movie.
Thank you so much for offering this product! It completed my collection.

I Love it, Thank You SSSSSSSSSOOOOOOOO Much!!!!!!
It's a great addition to my collection

Again Thank you
I didn't get the lenticular bonus card or the coin and it had a quite a few scratches on the disc itself but all in all it was ok.
